# Davisson窶敵ermer Experiment Example (Electron Diffraction)

This example implements the `DavissonGermerEngine` from `core/dg_engine.py` to simulate electron diffraction from a crystal and link the diffraction peak to the concepts of Visibility (V) and Distinguishability (D) within the DTQEM framework.

## Requirements

Same as the main project: Python 3.8+, numpy, scipy, matplotlib, ipywidgets.

Install with:
```bash
pip install numpy scipy matplotlib ipywidgets
